Add @absinthe{1%barspoon} to chilled #coupe and swirl it around the glass and discard remaining absinthe (known as a "rinse").

Build @gin{30%ml}, @cointreau{30%ml}, @Lillet Blanc{30%ml}, @fresh lemon juice{30%ml} in a #cocktail shaker{} with ice and shake for ~{15%seconds}. 

Strain into chilled #coupe glass{} and serve.
